@node main "Introduction to Port"

Port is another 'wrapper' object for a system structure - exec.library's
message port. This is used in inter-task communication such as intuition
or arexx.

There is an @{" autodoc " link EMODULES:oomodules/oodoc/guides/port/main} file available or this object.

To know more about message ports read the RKRM or take a look at the @{" AEE " link "AEE:exec/message ports.guide/main"} guide about it.
@endnode

@node where "Where to use this object"

Wherever you need a port.

@endnode

